AS3 UTILS
http://github.com/percentjuice/as3utils
common actionscript chores made simple.

INSTALLATION
This is an AS3 library, a compiled swc is included.  See LIBARARIES below for referenced libraries.  

LIBRARIES
AS3-Signals
https://github.com/robertpenner/as3-signals
Hamcrest-AS3
https://github.com/drewbourne/hamcrest-as3
AS3-Signals Utilities-Async
https://github.com/eidiot/as3-signals-utilities-async
Mockito_Flex
https://bitbucket.org/loomis/mockito-flex/wiki/Home

